{"tid":2157459,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"邱騰華不想做特首了 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-08-15T05:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T05:07:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"831e72aedec79e15860f8cfb35b66ba3a70a0c1b","tid":2157459,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/AEEL4WCU6ZBSPIYD6SEFOGJZTA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FAEEL4WCU6ZBSPIYD6SEFOGJZTA%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8fulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=76b03a5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FAEEL4WCU6ZBSPIYD6SEFOGJZTA%2F&h=8e597be9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/AEEL4WCU6ZBSPIYD6SEFOGJZTA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華不想做特首了 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aN-y2_YaGhSgq4FfOj0NtyUaf0E=/1280x990/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MZVOBAR5YRBAHKCC66KCSWTKPA.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaN-y2_YaGhSgq4FfOj0NtyUaf0E%3D%2F1280x990%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMZVOBAR5YRBAHKCC66KCSWTKPA.PNG&h=7ea13819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吃了豹子膽的美帝，近日未得特區政府首肯，即單方面宣布：。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n進入正題前，。。。。。。。。。例句：「阿源單方面宣布將與新桓結衣結婚」、「林鄭單方面宣布要與特朗普、蓬佩奧對談」，諸如此類。<br />\n<br />\n官方用語務必百分百精確，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n只要你不是文盲，也看得。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n一、一個人情急之下脫口而出的，通常只是成語，但「指白為黑」根本不是成語。若邱局長有心批評美國，最現成且準確的講法，是「指鹿為馬」而非「指白為黑」。用鹿馬代替黑白，不但常見得多，更不會褒港貶中。二、邱騰華答記者問時，曾以英語反問：「加拿大的產品可否標示為美國或墨西哥製造？」但加拿大是獨立國家，香港不是，這個顛三倒四的類比又是無心之失？請不要告訴我：無心就可以抹黑China、分裂國家。三、邱騰華並未就自己的用字不當、引喻失義而道歉。<br />\n<br />\n不道歉，即表示他是有心的。邱局長大概很害怕美國制裁，現在已無心爭做特首了，對不對？"}]}